from web pages, given that you respect the legal and ethical boundaries.\nWeb scraping means the automated extraction of data from the internet. While Python generally works fine for doing web scraping, the process itself is inherently ","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"POvKfvINg4"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"messy","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"NLrN7rDzmq"}],"key":"RvOx7cNb9K"},{"type":"text","value":"! Whenever you write a script to extract data from a certain website, you can be nearly sure that the same script won’t work a year from now. Or, if you are unlucky, it might not even work tomorrow.\nBut if you are lucky, someone else has gone through most of the pain for you and provides you with a proper ","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"xyesAaBgkB"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"API","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"rISavf9vuZ"}],"key":"mmHg3eBn4a"},{"type":"text","value":", maybe even a Python library (for instance the ","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"z68moVQ37l"},{"type":"link","url":"https://github.com/martin-majlis/Wikipedia-API","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wikipedia API","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"B2UW236Rv7"}],"urlSource":"https://github.com/martin-majlis/Wikipedia-API","error":true,"key":"RGKSvimUvC"},{"type":"text","value":").","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"GX6lw4vhiR"}],"key":"h8nzwH7SV4"}],"key":"KCLAU0VZlW"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Internal Corporate Data","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"qWgUP0N9bD"}],"key":"h0YwhhwRSV"},{"type":"text","value":": Picture a gold mine that a company sits upon; these are years’ worth of data that can unearth invaluable insights if analyzed correctly. Though if it is that promising, you probably will need a few lucky coincidences to get your hands on this piece of data ...","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"AEEiv1rBgo"}],"key":"ld4tameeTq"}],"key":"JCoAUsow8W"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Academic Data","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"gbvQoUzz0j"}],"key":"IhSTlzrZb6"},{"type":"text","value":": Scientifically collected and often meticulously maintained, these datasets can be found accompanying research papers. In many scientific disciplines it is becoming more and more common for authors to now only present and discuss their findings, but also to provide the data and/or the code used to extract those findings from the data (often termed: Open Science).","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"UOHdCvaXKw"}],"key":"hCOpoc8rDU"}],"key":"dbjQB8NbYp"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Data Upon Request","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"oSB9ovrkQc"}],"key":"Ya1oPQ0iFF"},{"type":"text","value":": Sometimes, just asking can open doors. Organizations might share data if approached correctly and for a worthy cause.","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"JKd1KYIeTz"}],"key":"TGodE6h9zK"}],"key":"nVoI8o0l3e"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Commercial Datasets","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"Vem4PWZkeM"}],"key":"aNrRerCiAo"},{"type":"text","value":": There are instances when investing in a dataset can prove to be more cost-effective than collecting data from scratch.","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"atPhUEArrb"}],"key":"Lf6z1nCzvF"}],"key":"ufBhsSgs6n"}],"key":"ZwmMazKjoR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Don’t let the typical course or tutorial situation trick you. In reality, you will rarely be in the comfortable position of receiving a large, high-quality dataset in an easy-to-import and easy-to-understand format. The most exciting data science projects usually do not come with a clean, ready-to-be-used csv file and well-documented metadata.","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"lbRYMRSwVE"}],"key":"qo50vG6j3o"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Often, the collection of data can be a major (and time-consuming!) part of the project itself. It can even happen that we need to reconsider some of our initial targets and strategies if we do not manage to collect the data as expected.","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"imR4ulCiwK"}],"key":"XOXnY5xyEq"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once we do hold the data in our hands (well, rather on a disk or cloud drive), we further need to make sure that the data is technically, legally, or quality-wise suitable for what we plan to do with the data in the following phases.","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"Ul0TfY7Fzd"}],"key":"XoljB6HuwM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once the data is in your hands, several pivotal steps ensure its quality and relevance:","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"zIl5k1oxhr"}],"key":"QVWlCOaBQX"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Data Format","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"YImjT9cBtR"}],"key":"jEl9qhlHAv"},{"type":"text","value":": Ensuring that the data is in a readable and workable format is paramount. Do you need to develop a custom parser, or can off-the-shelf software be used for ingestion?","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"srvFcB6QK5"}],"key":"NkUZy27Ijj"}],"key":"xjBiFlAeiy"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Source Credibility","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"wen7pSvrf7"}],"key":"mSY458tNOx"},{"type":"text","value":": If you have ever tried to collect data yourself, you will know that not all data is reliable. The credibility of the data source can significantly impact the reliability of your findings.","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"nAbow1ZwuI"}],"key":"tFmLu4XYCQ"}],"key":"BmZlgaj5Kh"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Data Processing Knowledge","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"sOBqNAAKv3"}],"key":"DVi2yoRU7Q"},{"type":"text","value":": A thorough understanding of how the data has been previously processed can save you from potential pitfalls. Valuable insights can often be gleaned from data processing logs or accompanying documentation.","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"K1wxQTPE15"}],"key":"YAP3rlcWlR"}],"key":"wpvKnB383y"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Legal issues:","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"UlAPcFeQC6"}],"key":"tMSAOusuiH"},{"type":"text","value":" Having data is not the same as ","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"WbiF1pbERB"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"being allowed to use it","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"c9jxf4SkBP"}],"key":"Z6ZYO6N26i"},{"type":"text","value":". Things like copyrights or privacy issues might render the data unfit for our goals.","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"mKgPX4Foe5"}],"key":"HtoO5zsKnQ"}],"key":"D17BcAvNdT"}],"key":"Rd2baS78Zq"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mini-Exercise: Hypothetical Scenario","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"kLEUcuSbrN"}],"key":"h6mokh7P2j"}],"identifier":"mini-exercise-hypothetical-scenario","label":"Mini-Exercise: Hypothetical Scenario","html_id":"mini-exercise-hypothetical-scenario","implicit":true,"key":"oOfFNgsGJ9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Imagine you are tasked with evaluating the state of digitization in schools in your region.","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"TInFc3jNgi"}],"key":"scBxemM6HM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Objective","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"NZ835TPW6B"}],"key":"kjMQQPGxBT"},{"type":"text","value":": Assess the current level of digital infrastructure and its utilization in schools.","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"bPyPzWpqtp"}],"key":"y9D65HU8I